description: Buddy up to your taste buds by treating them to BobbyDaddy’s delicious home-smoked meats. Bringing over 30 years of culinary experience to the food truck scene, Chef Bobbydaddy is a bonafide expert in quality comfort cuisine. You’ll taste the evidence when you take a bite of any of his beautifully delicious ‘BobbyQ,” like his Bacon-Wrapped BBQ Shrimp, Smoked Prime Rib Sandwich, or Baby Back BBQ Ribs. Famished folks of Florida, you must come by and try any item from this menu (we've only just named a few) and just know that “Your taste buds will thank you”.
name: BobbyDaddy's Food Truck
